{"tid":989982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南華早報教中國工廠利用香港&美國法律漏洞逃避闔稅","createTime":"2019-01-21T09:15:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T05:57:58.000Z","uid":14918,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"adddc563d1029a0dfc39167642701caf920228ec","tid":989982,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:15:01.000Z","msg":"SCMP原文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/2182215/trumps-trade-war-tariffs-send-firms-hong-kong-little-known\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Feconomy%2Fchina-economy%2Farticle%2F2182215%2Ftrumps-trade-war-tariffs-send-firms-hong-kong-little-known&d=w7%2FbDBVMSsXhjs7ptAmemE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8baa5e0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/2182215/trumps-trade-war-tariffs-send-firms-hong-kong-little-known</a><br />\nTrump&rsquo;s trade war tariffs send firms to Hong Kong for a little-known legal loophole<br />\n<br />\nIf you have a <span style=\"color: green;\">factory in China making smartphones</span>, you <span style=\"color: purple;\">sell that product first to your trading company in Hong Kong</span>. <span style=\"color: orange;\">Your Hong Kong trading company sells it on to the US, but Trump&rsquo;s tariffs are only payable on the first sale price &ndash; that is, what the trading company paid the factory.</span><br />\n<br />\n重點: 利用First Sale Rule + 香港獨立經濟禮<br />\n工廠象徵性$1賣貨給香港公司, 美國就只可以基於$1貨價下計算關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>綜合媒體2019年1月16日報道，中美貿易戰已對總計3,600億美元商品征稅，如按美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）提倡，讓美國企業將海外工廠轉移回美國；或是轉到亞洲其它國家，均非一日之功。 <br />\n<br />\n2019年1月16日，香港《南華早報》刊文《特朗普貿易戰有一法律漏洞，讓企業轉戰香港》報道稱，北京時間1月9日在中國香港，世界四大會計師事務所中的兩家普華永道（PwC）公司和德勤（Deloitte）公司召開約20位參與者的宣講會，主題是如何在香港避開中美貿易戰的關稅。 <br />\n<br />\n報道稱，會議談到美國有一條關稅法，從十九世紀八十年代的雷根（Ronald Reagan）總統時期開始執行，運用這條法律，在香港，企業可以避繳中美貿易戰的關稅，1988年香港企業首次通過這條法律，上訴獲得再轉運關稅豁免。 根據美國國際貿易委員會規定，如果在進口到美國前，商品交易超過一次，則適用&ldquo;海關完稅價格法（First Sale Rule，簡稱完稅法）&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，完稅法適用已經售出、在途的美國進口商品，舉例來說，如果一部手機在大陸生產，賣給香港貿易代理商，當再次出售給美國時，只要能夠出具必要的完稅采購單以及大陸企業透明度調查證明，就不必再次繳納關稅，因為特朗普的關稅僅對從未繳稅的中國商品生效。 <br />\n<br />\n報道稱，現代貨箱碼頭公司是香港歷史最久、第二大貨櫃碼頭運營商，集團董事總經理萊維斯克（Peter Levesque）稱：&ldquo;香港的海運，有70%是轉運貨物。貨進香港，再去中國其它地區，或是去往世界各地。&rdquo; 報道稱，香港科技奢侈品配件公司本土聯盟的首席財務官梅爾祖吉（Farouk Merzougui）表示，申請免稅流程非常繁瑣，需要五個月時間，但是出口到美國的商品，省下了三分之二的稅。 梅爾祖吉說：&ldquo;當時是為了聖誕銷售旺季的訂單，我們想在短期替換辦法與長期供應鏈的解決辦法之間，找到平穩過渡的橋梁，但基於那時的情況，（用完稅法）是短期最好的辦法。&rdquo; 梅爾祖吉補充說：&ldquo;10%的關稅還能夠駕馭，25%的關稅就是生存還是毀滅的事了。&rdquo;  </blockquote>"},{"pid":"e5e69f519589c60e30ffb613e88d17cda16f89cb","tid":989982,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:17:08.000Z","msg":"標題係關稅先真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440a25d40e53295ffea377e1f5250c41331d1d9d","tid":989982,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"闔稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e94e869c1b418d24ad7974e52df2e99018223a","tid":989982,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"440a25d40e53295ffea377e1f5250c41331d1d9d","tid":989982,"uid":131522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:23:32.000Z","msg":"闔稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:33:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/989982/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/989982/page/1</a><br />\n#2"},{"pid":"d41a02d76a7588135b0f010973b56a3c50d80f02","tid":989982,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3691110c6b0448f15